, 
<geoCoordinate degrees="98" direction="east" minutes="26" orientation="longitude" precision="15" seconds="46" value="98.44611">98°26'46&quot;E</geoCoordinate>
, 2667 m alt., 1 September 2015, 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="25">X.Y.Ye YXY272</emphasis>
(holotype &amp; isotype: KUN!).
